

1. Create a virtual env & make sure you have `virtualenv` installed
	`virtualenv venv`

2. Enable VENV => source venv/bin/activate

3. Install requirements
	`pip install -r requirements.txt`

4. Install Node Modules this will create node modules
	`npm install`

4. Run Djnago server
	`python manage.py runserver`

5. Run Webpack Watcher
	`npm run hot`

